<h1>Fake news is news, stories or hoaxes created to deliberately misinform or deceive readers</h4>
<h1>The purpose behind people creating fake news are most often to change peoples views on certain topics. But some people spread fake news because by spreading fake news they would be earning tons and tons of money. Here is an example video of how people benefit from the spread of fake news and how to prevent it:-</h1>
